{"tid":82334,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"平紀錄，C朗射入西甲最多12碼","createTime":"2017-01-16T00:44:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T17:53:08.000Z","uid":44925,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"875fb85fd7c8f5e4171062a972a5d033b229780c","tid":82334,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T00:44:55.000Z","msg":"皇馬在客場1-2負于西維爾，雖然終結了不敗紀錄，但C朗卻在個人紀錄上有所突破，他追平了曉高-山齊斯，成為西甲歷史上射入12碼最多的球員。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在皮斯胡安球場球場，C朗用點球為皇馬首開記錄，這是他在西甲打進的第56個12碼。<br />\n<br />\nC朗已經在249場西甲聯賽中主罰了65個12碼，而墨西哥傳奇曉高-山齊斯這一數據為347場主罰71球，罰失15球，顯然C羅命中率更高一些。<br />\n<br />\n不算上12碼大戰的數字，C朗已經為皇馬在各項賽事中主罰了82個12碼，打入69個。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n恭喜C朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f1ac6e00e77b93bf130a15e6f0bfe5a878410b","tid":82334,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T01:46:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://video.skysports.com/Q4OGJ4ODE6OiB_PK5d5EC1F7nVpai0uf/MGngRNnbuHoiqTJH4xMDoxOjBzMTt2bJ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.skysports.com%2FQ4OGJ4ODE6OiB_PK5d5EC1F7nVpai0uf%2FMGngRNnbuHoiqTJH4xMDoxOjBzMTt2bJ&h=9ea55494&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5fe250552626e75b2d25e89f8236c986c83ad8c5","tid":82334,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T01:47:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e51045334167cc13ead7e8e391f3cd74a150fb","tid":82334,"uid":19322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T01:50:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/16/095029_7f52dd6914c01c485864936a591ca018.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F16%2F095029_7f52dd6914c01c485864936a591ca018.jpg&h=49677164&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9dea55e622f550f15a99c63bbc2f067c5244e6c8","tid":82334,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T02:0