ac581fb&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n整爛個草皮好似係</blockquote><br />\nCheck ball</blockquote><br />\n個球證唔叫個西維爾球員遠離12碼點，C朗又唔搵球證投訴，到出咗手，個球證都仲係無影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n踢波同個波有少少接觸好正常姐<br />\n俾個波掂下都唔得,死返去打乒乓球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"061ff47aeedfd14d26e2760d081b07dd2e110c6c","tid":82334,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T08:11:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問發生咩事，點解球王射12碼嘅時候同對面爭執？主持12碼但球證失蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/l0ExgGP0JRbCIu66A/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Fl0ExgGP0JRbCIu66A%2Fgiphy.gif&h=3ac581fb&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n整爛個草皮好似係</blockquote><br />\nCheck ball</blockquote><br />\n個球證唔叫個西維爾球員遠離12碼點，C朗又唔搵球證投訴，到出咗手，個球證都仲係無影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n踢波同個波有少少接觸好正常姐<br />\n俾個波掂下都唔得,死返去打乒乓球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n阻住朗哥破紀錄抵打啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"342fc5772cdfb6de178f1a4c95c07d201f7bb884","tid":82334,"uid":2538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T08:37:50.000Z","msg":"咁對住唔識射12碼既美斯做對手，c朗破記錄的確係無乜難度既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6bf9419143e0b36ead4b6901e3b49f4587bab74","tid":82334,"uid":76314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:43:56.000Z","msg":"型到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c39fc2e522318a71799b0a950a80c89f241363bd","tid":82334,"uid":52087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco